        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 4 at 3:48PM MDT by NWS Pueblo CO</headline>
        <description>HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Boaters in John Martin Reservoir should be prepared for
very strong winds of 50 mph.

Locations impacted include...
Las Animas, Hasty, John Martin Reservoir, Blue Lake, Fort Lyon, and
Caddoa.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
